      "para_id": "Q004136.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Lu-Nanna , the scribe , child of Inim-Šara , land recorder of the king , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
